   |   Beep         Silence      - <Beep whenever program pauses>   |
   |                                                                |
   +----------------------------------------------------------------+

The Beep option causes the program to beep whenever it pauses after
the plot or after the tables.  This is useful if you are doing
something else why the computer computes.  On the other hand, if you
are carefully watching the computer screen, the beep is annoying.
Silence is golden.